() provided in the latter that . This was the first
indication that some of the trajectories of the WQO are the same
as those of the canonical Bose oscillator. The question is  how
far does this similarity go. In the next proposition we summarize
the results which we are able to establish.

 
To each  mean trajectory in the
phase space of the Wigner quantum oscillator there corresponds an
identical trajectory of the 3D Bose canonical quantum oscillator.

